{"tid":690394,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識死仲要簽森巴兵！曼聯唔好累己累人","createTime":"2018-06-04T23:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T07:09:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0518d7914801d1ac052fc7d66ce05eb7b13b0b26","tid":690394,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:22:58.000Z","msg":"如無意外，曼聯將會簽入巴西國腳費特，有猛將加盟，一眾紅魔躉梗係開心啦。不過，希望愈大往往失望愈大，大家仲記得基巴臣、路爾斯安達臣、達施華兄弟嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n曼聯史上甚少出現巴西球員，而且都係失敗收場，經典代表一定係基巴臣。呢位中場於2003年同C朗一齊加盟曼聯，成為兩人球員生涯轉捩點，當年小伙子C朗從此平步青雲，但身為巴西2002世界盃冠軍成員嘅基巴臣，卻直插谷底，兩季加埋上陣僅20次就執包袱，輾轉返巴西搵食。 <br />\n<br />\n而一度被捧為「新細哨」嘅路爾斯安達臣同樣雷聲大雨點小，效力曼聯8年冇作為，連自己體重都控制唔到，又係打道回府返巴西，佢同基巴臣被指為費格遜十大最失敗收購。 <br />\n<br />\n至於達施華兄弟冒起都係曇花一現，拉菲爾達施華依家踢熙里昂，法比奧達施華更加搞到要去英冠搵食。唔知身價達5300萬鎊(約5.6億港元)嘅費特，又可以捱到幾耐呢？"},{"pid":"64e0709dc55f37edf8e5566545ca4265c474b8c6","tid":690394,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"王蛇病好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc619dc3c9c8c0db87ab834cb41dd369393e1018","tid":690394,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64e0709dc55f37edf8e5566545ca4265c474b8c6","tid":690394,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"王蛇病好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:37:25.000Z","msg":"未，喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34175611c948d0fca08434f222af838e01070e38","tid":690394,"uid":19126,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"達施華兄弟係傷影響姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拉非耳真心好球員黎，我好鍾意佢，係敢帥個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n安達神夾硬拎黎做工兵就梗係衰，呢個係費sir打442走去買攻中迫人適應既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n費sir手下既攻中打得廢唔代表真係廢，只係唔岩位<br />\n<br />\n翼打得廢呢，就真係廢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},{"pid":"bd95d62e03593d623fc0e6a90910f71ac3566bff","tid":690394,"uid":41908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰件真係垃圾"},{"pid":"3ffa952ccba276d656d290338ae66709f3babc58","tid":690394,"uid":60479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"no, 中場踢薩克達, 今年世界盃都有選入國家隊"},{"pid":"80e09f6f3b21dd91af867869a3d6980939f30715","tid":690394,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"果個牙FRED踢中超都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5253e726524f500b0b1be4296ddfb1b420298ee6","tid":690394,"uid":37735,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得浸過東歐浸水的巴西佬 <br />\n係英超踢得會ok<br />\n<br />\n好像薩克達 的william, fernando<br />\n去車，曼城都好岩用<br />\n<br />\n呢種巴西人 無咁嬌生慣養 無咁文化圍爐<br />\n習慣左唔係接近巴西的劣質