es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ea41a4862ae8daaa5cf37dc1dabf7cd5ed207a","tid":690394,"uid":120232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得浸過東歐浸水的巴西佬 <br />\n係英超踢得會ok<br />\n<br />\n好像薩克達 的william, fernando<br />\n去車，曼城都好岩用<br />\n<br />\n呢種巴西人 無咁嬌生慣養 無咁文化圍爐<br />\n習慣左唔係接近巴西的劣質南歐文化堆生活(以西，葡為代表 意粉某程度都係)<br />\n<br />\n巴西球員去東歐生活 支援 同鄉 文化適應  絕對難過西歐  咁都捱到出來  <br />\n性格上應該唔會太有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD Costa 係薩克達去拜仁都算ok<br />\n有人話巴西人去英格蘭很難適應天氣，但烏克蘭仲凍過英國，可能鍛鍊到克苦耐勞 ，所以佢地幾個去英超算發展得好<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 耶穌去到曼城算勁，第一次出國係曼城已經踢得唔錯"},{"pid":"ab2ddca2b7a29dcdea3fb97dcbae9305fcc9dd8e","tid":690394,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd95d62e03593d623fc0e6a90910f71ac3566bff","tid":690394,"uid":41908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰件真係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"嗰個叫特癈，吖唔係，係費特"},{"pid":"79c90e2fbe6506eff60670ac01ea2d72df88a861","tid":690394,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2ddca2b7a29dcdea3fb97dcbae9305fcc9dd8e","tid":690394,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd95d62e03593d623fc0e6a90910f71ac3566bff","tid":690394,"uid":41908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4df9a1413d6f4e07f67757774367474ffcc04fb","tid":690394,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"係咪14世界盃個9號"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰件真係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:55:56.000Z","msg":